      "content": "\"keep me engaged and invested\"... that's just a nice way of saying they're buying my silence, isn't it? Like, if I'm busy managing this new role and sitting in this fancy office, I'm too distracted to actually investigate the things I saw in the compliance reports. It feels less like a reward and more like a golden cage. Do you think they're actually watching my every move now that I'm more \"valuable\"?",
